Date: april 2012
License: [MIT-license](https://github.com/avdgaag/#{NAME}/blob/master/LICENSE) (same as Ruby)
EOS

create_file 'HISTORY.md', <<-EOS
# HISTORY

## 0.1.0

* Initial release

EOS

